# iOS builds use the same production bundle as the website: `pnpm build` loads `.env.production`
# (not this file unless you add a custom Vite mode). Copy these values into `.env.production`, then:
#   pnpm build && pnpm cap:sync
#
# CORS on the API uses * so Capacitor origins work (AWS does not allow capacitor:// in AllowOrigins).

# Cognito (from CDK stack output)
# VITE_COGNITO_USER_POOL_ID=us-east-1_9jr8u8h37
# VITE_COGNITO_CLIENT_ID=3aatm24d4c0r2qtt57jnfoutod
# VITE_COGNITO_OAUTH_DOMAIN=repwise785874435982.auth.us-east-1.amazoncognito.com

# API: custom domain from CDK output ApiUrl
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://api.repwisefit.com

# AI workout generation (SSE): Lambda Function URL from CDK output AiWorkoutStreamUrl
# VITE_AI_WORKOUT_STREAM_URL=https://xxxxxxxxxx.lambda-url.us-east-1.on.aws/
